    "MeasureNumber": 3450,
    "CatchLine": "Allows city with population greater than 75,000 not within metropolitan service district to adopt changes to its comprehensive plan and land use regulations authorizing mixed-use housing within up to 40 acres of lands zoned for employment uses.",
